## 3. Technical Component Breakdown & Tech Stack

To build a version that looks "even better," we will use a premium modern stack that guarantees fast load times, excellent SEO, and smooth micro-animations.

*   **Framework:** Next.js (App Router) - For SSR, SEO, and fast routing.
*   **Language:** TypeScript - For type safety and better developer experience.
*   **Styling:** Tailwind CSS - For rapid, utility-first styling.
*   **UI Components:** shadcn/ui & Radix UI - For accessible, high-quality, unstyled components (Modals, Carousels, Forms, Sheets) that we can theme beautifully.
*   **Animations:** Framer Motion - To add premium micro-animations (e.g., fade-in on scroll, smooth modal popups, interactive hover states on service cards).
*   **Icons:** Lucide React.

